Loyiso Mkize, who is famed for his work on comic book Supa Strikas shares his journey in the world of visual arts. As the mind behind current locally produces comic book, Kwezi, Mkize shares how he has made life changing decisions that have ensured his ever soaring career. For more episodes,click here. Do you have an inspiring story to tell? Are you an entrepreneur making big moves? Do you know of a small business that needs more support? Share your stories with us via e-mail sebenza@sowetanlive.co.za or reach out to us on social media @SebenzaLIVE on Twitter or Instagram. Subscribe: iono.fm | Spotify | Pocket Casts | Player.fm